profile:
Operating since 1986, Southwestern Ontario's premier installer for irrigation systems and synthetic turf putting greens and synthetic turf landscaping.  
During the winter months we also offer snow removal services to commercial and residential properties in the London area.   

For our irrigation systems we provide products manufactured by Rainbird and Hunter. 
For artificial grass surfaces, we specialize in creating your dream backyard oasis. 

We install pet turf, landscape turf and synthetic putting greens.
We use a sand infill process which is second to none backed by Rymars 8 year warranty.

Get in Touch
Toll Free 1-800-361-4074
